jdbwctest
Class CoreTest

java.lang.Object
  jdbwctest.CoreTest

public class CoreTest
extends java.lang.Object

This class is designed for JDBWC-1.0.0.2-beta
You will need the JDBWC-1.0.0.2.jar file and its bundled jdbwc-lib folder to use this class.
If you dont have either, go here to get a copy: http://jdbwc.sourceforge.net

To run this class call its main method. Params will be ignored.

This class contains testing methods to demonstrate basic JDBWC use.

We are only using Strings for output in this demo but a JDBWC ResultSet can currently handle outputing Objects, Strings, number classes, date related classes and bytes (although not byte arrays yet).
There may also be a few ive missed.
Most other data types are not fully implemented.
The inline comments in this class's source-file explain more.
